Date: 1999-02-08

Title: Anharmonic Oscillators, Spectral Determinant and Short Exact Sequence of

affine U_q(sl_2)Authors: J. Suzuki(University of Tokyo at Komaba)

Comments: 8 pages, Latex 2e

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) L183-L188

We prove one of conjectures, raised by Dorey and Tateo in the connectionamong the spectral determinant of anharmonic oscillator and vacuum eigenvaluesof transfer matrices in field theory and statistical mechanics. The exactsequence of $U_q(\hat{sl}_2)$ plays a fundamental role in the proof.